    '[[$researchPostNews]]' => '<!--researchPost-->
<div class="sixteen columns two-thirds column omega" id="report_container">
<div><a href="index.php?id=82" id="blog_title"><h3>Eastern Promise</h3></a>
</div>
<div class="two-thirds column alpha"><img class="lazy" src="/living_octave_research/assets/research assets/design/images/130830_store-Clerk_Jiang-Qiong.png" alt="image" data-original=[[+image]] /></div>
<div id="newsfeed_source"><p>Financial Times</p></div>
<div id="report_download"><a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/bd3a4a54-a12f-11e2-990c-00144feabdc0.html" title="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/bd3a4a54-a12f-11e2-990c-00144feabdc0.html" target="_blank">Read the Article</a> <br />(<a href="/living_octave_research/assets/research assets/design/articles/130830_Eastern promise_Financial Times.pdf" title="/living_octave_research/assets/research assets/design/articles/130830_Eastern promise_Financial Times.pdf" target="_blank">Download</a>)</div>
<div id="main_story_teaser"><p><em><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></em></p>
<p><em><span style="color: #000000;">“<span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;">There’s a growing audience for Chinese brands – it’s more lifestyle and homeware products at the moment, but that could change.”</span></span></em></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span>China\'s emerging design stars are gaining the attention of global brands and global markets. Designer Xiao Li recently received the Diesel Award for her runway show in </span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;">Trieste, Italy and </span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span> Hermès and designer Jiang Qiong are opening up </span></span></span><a title="China Daily" href="http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/2012-02/08/content_14562024.htm" target="_blank">a flagship store in Paris this fall</a><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span> under the Shang Xia brand. All indicative of a shift in perception of Chinese products as well as a commercial recognition that Chinese brands can compete with European brands on an international stage.</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span> </span></span></span></p>
<p><img title="Xiao Li" src="assets/research%20assets/design/images/130830_Double_Xiao-Li.png" alt="Xiao Li" width="620" height="467" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">“<span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span>The reputation for cheap production was driven by demand from western brands wanting lower-priced goods but China has a long history of craftsmanship and creating high quality, luxury products.”</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span> </span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span>Jiang Qiong, as much philosopher as she is designer dismisses the term luxury as a marketing gimmick. “The true luxuries of today are time and emotion.” </span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span><span> </span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span><span><img title="Jiang Qiong" src="assets/research%20assets/design/images/130830_Portrait-Two_Jiang-Qiong.png" alt="Jiang Qiong" width="620" height="450" /><span> </span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span><span> </span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span><span>Read more of her interview on The <a title="The Brander" href="http://www.thebrander.com/article.php?o=555" target="_blank">Brander</a></span></span></span></span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span>See more from Xiao Li\'s RCA collection at </span></span></span><a title="Dezeen" href="http://www.dezeen.com/2013/06/05/rca-fashion-2013-collection-by-xiao-li/" target="_blank">Dezeen</a><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span>.</span></span></span></p></div>
<div id="frontpage_story_meta">by Timothy Voice, on 08/30</div>

</div><!--end report_container-->',
